Magic Years Child Care andLearning Centers Inc said it signed a letter of intent toacquire three profitable day care centers in south centralPennsylvania for a total price of 350,000 dlrs.    The three privately owned centers had aggregate revenues of474,000 dlrs in 1986, with profits of six thousand dlrs, thecompany said.    The transaction is scheduled to close in early July, thecompany said. Reuter&#3;